    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice </strong>and <strong>cauliflower rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 110ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[175ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[225ml] </span>cold water and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/korean-style-lean-beef-bulgogi-with-beans-and-cauliflower-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, trim, then cut your <strong>green beans</strong> in half</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/korean-style-lean-beef-bulgogi-with-beans-and-cauliflower-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely, keeping the <strong>white parts</strong> and <strong>green parts</strong> separate</p><p>Grate your <strong>apple[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(skin on) into a large bowl and discard the core[s]</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/korean-style-lean-beef-bulgogi-with-beans-and-cauliflower-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>mince</strong>,<strong> chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion whites</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> and 2 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp] </span><strong>brown</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>sugar</strong> to the grated apple and mix thoroughly with clean hands \u2013 this is your <strong>Korean-style mince</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/korean-style-lean-beef-bulgogi-with-beans-and-cauliflower-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> Korean-style mince</strong> and the <strong>halved green beans</strong></p><p>Spread the mixture out and cook for 4 min, without stirring</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/korean-style-lean-beef-bulgogi-with-beans-and-cauliflower-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Flip the meat, and cook for a further 4 min on the other side (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once cooked, break up the <strong>mince</strong> into rough bite-sized pieces with a wooden spoon \u2013 this is your <strong>Korean-style bulgogi with beans</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/korean-style-lean-beef-bulgogi-with-beans-and-cauliflower-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add most of the <strong>sliced spring onion greens</strong> (save some for garnish!) to the cooked rice, fluff with a fork and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/korean-style-lean-beef-bulgogi-with-beans-and-cauliflower-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Korean-style lean beef bulgogi with beans</strong> with the <strong>cooked cauliflower</strong> <strong>rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> reserved sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
